Problem Statement:
Given a sorted array consisting 0’s and 1’s. The task is to find the index of first ‘1’ in the given array.

Solution:
public long firstIndex(long arr[], long n)
    {
        long result=-1;
        for(int i=0;i<n;++i)
        {
            if(arr[i]==1)
            {
                result=i;
                break;
            }
        }
        return result;
    }
